data.description: Priced to Sell! Fully Remodeled and modernized with Solar! Perfect for a first time buyer or investor. This 3 bedroom, 3 bath, 1 car garage and 1 carport 2 story condo is located in SW Visalia in a quiet community. This condo features Freshly painted throughout home with vaulted ceilings in the living room with gas fireplace, kitchen nook with stainless steal sunken sink, laminate flooring from bottom to top and in between (stair flooring)! Enjoy your showers in your newly remodeled tiled bathrooms!  Balcony access from master bedroom great for morning coffee and evening book readings as the sunsets to the west. Easy backyard access through your new back fence to community pool, park and picnic area. Must see! Contact your local realtor for personal showing!
